---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for Turf Tech HQ — the rules and guidelines governing your use of our landscaping resource website.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 font-heading">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text">
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
          Welcome to Turf Tech HQ. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the turftechhq.com website (the "Site"), operated by Turf Tech HQ ("we," "us," or "our"). By accessing or using the Site, you agree to be bound by these Terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          By accessing or using the Site, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, you must not use the Site.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Use of the Site</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not infringe the rights of, restrict, or inhibit anyone else's use and enjoyment of the Site. Specifically, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Use the Site in any way that breaches any applicable local, national, or international law or regulation</li>
          <li>Transmit or send any material that is defamatory, offensive, or otherwise objectionable</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Site</li>
          <li>Use the Site to transmit viruses, malware, or any other malicious code</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate, copy, or resell any part of the Site without our express written permission</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Content</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.1 Information Only</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The content on Turf Tech HQ is provided for general informational and educational purposes only. All information on the Site is provided in good faith; however, we make no representation or warranty of any kind, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, adequacy, validity, reliability, availability, or completeness of any information on the Site.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.2 Not Professional Advice</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The Site content is not intended to be a substitute for professional landscaping advice, diagnosis, or installation services. Always seek the advice of a qualified landscaping professional with any questions you may have. Never disregard professional advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this Site.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.3 Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The Site and its original content, features, and functionality are and shall remain the exclusive property of Turf Tech HQ and its licensors. The Site is protected by copyright, trademark, and other laws.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Affiliate Links &amp; Advertising</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">4.1 Amazon Associates</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Turf Tech HQ participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. Product links may be affiliate links, meaning we earn a commission if you make a purchase through them at no additional cost to you.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">4.2 Google AdSense</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The Site displays advertisements through Google AdSense. We do not endorse or guarantee any products or services advertised on the Site. Ad content is managed by Google and subject to Google's own policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Email Newsletter</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          By subscribing to our email newsletter, you consent to receive periodic emails containing landscaping tips, guides, and updates. You may unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email or by contacting us via our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-light hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Turf Tech HQ shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including without limitation, loss of profits, data, goodwill, or other intangible losses, resulting from your access to or use of (or inability to access or use) the Site.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective upon posting to the Site. Your continued use of the Site following any changes constitutes acceptance of those changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us through our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-light hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Turf Tech HQ</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
